---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import dashboard from '../../../assets/photos/caldaie1.webp';
import adCreativa from '../../../assets/photos/caldaie2.webp';

const calendlyUrl = 'https://app.reclaim.ai/m/davide-veneto/call-conoscitiva';
---

<Layout
	lang="en"
	title="100k+ sales/month in boilers with less than 2,500 invested | Davide Veneto"
	description="How we brought an HVAC company to sell over 100k in boilers per month with less than 2,500 in ad spend."
>
	<section class="pt-32 pb-20 md:pt-40 md:pb-28 relative">
		<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
			<a href="/en/" class="text-red font-heading text-sm tracking-[0.2em] mb-6 inline-block hover:text-red-glow transition-colors">&larr; BACK TO HOME</a>
			<p class="text-red font-heading text-lg tracking-[0.2em] mb-4">HVAC</p>
			<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-heading leading-[0.95] mb-6">
				100k+ in sales/month<br />
				<span class="text-red">with less than 2,500 invested</span>
			</h1>
			<p class="text-gray-300 text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed">
				How we helped Fabio sell over 100,000 in boilers per month, starting from campaigns that weren't working.
			</p>
			<div class="w-20 h-1 bg-red mt-8"></div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-black-light border-t border-b border-white/5">
		<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
			<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading mb-8">The initial <span class="text-red">situation</span></h2>
			<div class="space-y-6 text-gray-300 text-lg leading-relaxed">
				<p>Fabio runs an HVAC company in Lombardy, mainly focused on boiler installation.</p>
				<div class="grid gap-4 mt-4">
					<div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-5 bg-black-card border border-gray-700/50">
						<span class="text-red font-heading text-xl">&#10005;</span>
						<p class="text-gray-300">Ad campaigns were bringing contacts at 50 each</p>
					</div>
					<div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-5 bg-black-card border border-gray-700/50">
						<span class="text-red font-heading text-xl">&#10005;</span>
						<p class="text-gray-300">Word of mouth wasn't enough to keep all teams busy (he had recently hired two new technicians)</p>
					</div>
					<div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-5 bg-black-card border border-gray-700/50">
						<span class="text-red font-heading text-xl">&#10005;</span>
						<p class="text-gray-300">The situation was becoming stressful</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="py-16 md:py-24">
		<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
			<div class="section-divider mb-8"></div>
			<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading mb-8">What <span class="text-red">I did</span></h2>
			<div class="space-y-4">
				<div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-5 bg-black-card border border-gray-700/50">
					<span class="text-red font-heading text-2xl">01</span>
					<p class="text-gray-300">Analyzed the bottleneck: the previous agency had done a good job, but it wasn't suited to the current market scenario.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-5 bg-black-card border border-gray-700/50">
					<span class="text-red font-heading text-2xl">02</span>
					<p class="text-gray-300">Analyzed competitors: what they were saying, which offers they were promoting.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-5 bg-black-card border border-gray-700/50">
					<span class="text-red font-heading text-2xl">03</span>
					<p class="text-gray-300">Found a strong differentiator and built an irresistible offer. People want a turnkey boiler installation.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-black-light border-t border-b border-white/5">
		<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
			<div class="section-divider mb-8"></div>
			<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading mb-8">The <span class="text-red">journey</span></h2>
			<div class="space-y-8">
				<div class="relative pl-8 border-l-2 border-red/30">
					<span class="absolute -left-3 top-0 w-6 h-6 bg-red rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold">1</span>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-heading text-white mb-3">First month</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">Campaigns start working, but contacts are still few. Fabio gets discouraged and thinks about going back to lead portals. I understand the situation: campaigns were profitable, but not enough for all the sales reps.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="relative pl-8 border-l-2 border-red/30">
					<span class="absolute -left-3 top-0 w-6 h-6 bg-red rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold">2</span>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-heading text-white mb-3">Second month — The turning point</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">I read the data and realize that in Fabio's area, many contacts are over 50 years old and very skeptical about price and service.</p>
					<p class="text-white font-semibold">I adapt the ads to the audience, writing copy that anticipates their objections.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="py-16 md:py-24">
		<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
			<div class="section-divider mb-8"></div>
			<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading mb-8">The <span class="text-red">results</span></h2>
			<div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6">
				<div class="p-6 bg-red/10 border border-red/30 text-center">
					<p class="text-gray-500 text-sm line-through mb-1">CPA: 30</p>
					<p class="text-red font-heading text-4xl mb-2">13</p>
					<p class="text-white">Cost per contact</p>
				</div>
				<div class="p-6 bg-red/10 border border-red/30 text-center">
					<p class="text-red font-heading text-4xl mb-2">3x</p>
					<p class="text-white">Contacts tripled</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="p-6 bg-black-card border border-gray-700/50">
				<div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-center">
					<div>
						<p class="text-red font-heading text-2xl">1,600</p>
						<p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">invested</p>
					</div>
					<div>
						<p class="text-red font-heading text-2xl">108</p>
						<p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">contacts</p>
					</div>
					<div>
						<p class="text-red font-heading text-2xl">26</p>
						<p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">boilers sold</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-8">
				<div>
					<p class="text-red font-heading text-sm tracking-wider mb-3">CAMPAIGN DASHBOARD</p>
					<img src={(dashboard as any).src ?? dashboard} alt="Meta campaigns dashboard boilers" class="w-full rounded border border-gray-700/50" />
				</div>
				<div>
					<p class="text-red font-heading text-sm tracking-wider mb-3">THE AD CREATIVE</p>
					<img src={(adCreativa as any).src ?? adCreativa} alt="Boiler ads creative" class="w-full rounded border border-gray-700/50" />
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-black-light border-t border-b border-white/5">
		<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
			<div class="section-divider mb-8"></div>
			<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading mb-8">Takeaways <span class="text-red">for you</span></h2>
			<div class="grid gap-4">
				<div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-5 bg-black-card border border-gray-700/50">
					<span class="text-red font-heading text-xl">&rarr;</span>
					<p class="text-gray-300">Invest with someone who brings you <strong class="text-white">sales</strong>, not visibility</p>
				</div>
				<div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-5 bg-black-card border border-gray-700/50">
					<span class="text-red font-heading text-xl">&rarr;</span>
					<p class="text-gray-300">Use the <strong class="text-white">double sales rep</strong> technique: if they don't accept the first quote, have another person call with a limited-time offer</p>
				</div>
				<div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-5 bg-black-card border border-gray-700/50">
					<span class="text-red font-heading text-xl">&rarr;</span>
					<p class="text-gray-300">Create an <strong class="text-white">irresistible offer</strong>: not a rock-bottom price, but services and bonuses that increase value for the customer</p>
				</div>
				<div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-5 bg-black-card border border-gray-700/50">
					<span class="text-red font-heading text-xl">&rarr;</span>
					<p class="text-gray-300">Offer a <strong class="text-white">turnkey service</strong> and recontact people as soon as possible</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="py-24 md:py-40 bg-red relative overflow-hidden">
		<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center relative">
			<div class="w-20 h-1 bg-white/30 mb-8 mx-auto"></div>
			<h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading mb-6 text-white">Want similar results<br />for your business?</h2>
			<p class="text-white/80 text-lg mb-10">Book a free 30-minute call. Let's analyze your situation together.</p>
			<a href={calendlyUrl} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-primary-inverted">Book a strategy call</a>
		</div>
	</section>

	<footer class="py-8 border-t border-gray-700/30">
		<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
			<p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">&copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} Power Adv di Veneto Davide. All rights reserved.</p>
		</div>
	</footer>
</Layout>
